  "title": "Business Analyst (Banking)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Qualifications and Profile</strong></u></p><ul><li>Candidates should have1-2 years’ experience in Business Analysis activities.</li><li>Knowledge of Static Data, Workflows, Confirmations, Settlements, Messages / Swift messages, Positions, Accounting, Corporate action, Filters, Reporting Framwork,Reconciliation features.</li><li>Understanding of financial assets (FX, Money Market, cash products) and trade lifecycle.</li><li>Experience with regulatory reporting (e.g. HRF, NORIA, MMSR).</li><li>Experience on Back Office systems</li><li>Experience in interfacing systems</li><li>Familiar with requirements life cycle management, analysis planning and monitoring, requirements’ analysis and design definition.</li><li>Hands-on experience as liaison function between the onshore IT business lines and offshore technical teams and as primary functional support for development team</li></ul><p>To Apply:</p><p>Interested applicants please send your resume in MS Words\nformat to <a href=\"mailto:pooja.yadav@ambition.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">pooja.yadav@ambition.com.sg</a> and\nattention to <strong>Pooja (R1551322)</strong></p><p>Short listed candidates will be notified</p><p><a href=\"http://www.ambition.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.ambition.com.sg</a></p><p>EA Registration Number: R1551322</p><p>Data provided is for recruitment purposes only</p><p>Business Registration Number: 200611680D. <br />License Number: 10C5117</p>",
